"no", "when": "2016-04-25T11:42:22Z", "uid": "i0jhi7iynx514d", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "infbmzmzzxm6m1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T12:06:43Z", "uid": "i6swz3atggR", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "infbmzmzzxm6m1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T12:22:56Z", "uid": "i6swz3atggR", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "infbmzmzzxm6m1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T12:50:22Z", "uid": "hxfr6dv2fy44k8", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "infbmzmzzxm6m1", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T13:56:37Z", "uid": "i6vkcot30qG", "type": "followup"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "infbmzmzzxm6m1", "bookmarked": 30, "no_answer_followup": 25, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:33:10Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "ikwla6afpqb", "created": "2016-04-25T01:33:10Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infbxqn4r6f1ul", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>2013011331黄欢</p>\n<p>2013011425蔡文静</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>没有choosing时&#xff1a;有T1&#xff0c;T2&#xff0c;初始num[1]=num[2]=0&#xff0c;首先num[2]=1&#xff08;进入临界区&#xff09;&#xff0c;然后num[1]=1&#xff0c;也进入临界区。</p>\n<p>图示如下&#xff1a;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/ikwla6afpqb/infbu4293wga/ans.png\" /></p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:33:47Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "created": "2016-04-25T01:33:47Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infbyjngfne37l", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T05:02:33Z", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "created": "2016-04-25T05:02:33Z", "type": "feedback", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infjf0dmuqc2nm", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p></p>\n<p>张明瑞 2013011391</p>\n<p>吴之璟 2013011392</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/DrustZ/OS_SPOC_hw/blob/master/hw16/spoc.md\" target=\"_blank\">SPOC 问答题</a></p>"}], "subject": "<p>没有choosing的时候&#xff0c;假设ab两个进程&#xff0c;pid a  &lt; pid b</p>\n<p>此时开始&#xff0c;假设a已经运行过critical区域&#xff0c;然后number[a] = 0; 这时候b进行number[b] 的赋值&#xff0c;</p>\n<p>number[b] = max(number) &#43; 1, 但是在赋值的过程中进行被打断&#xff0c;然后</p>\n<p>接下来a开始进行number[a] 赋值&#xff0c;number[a] = max(number) &#43; 1,但是赋值过程中又被打断&#xff0c;</p>\n<p>然后切换到b = 1进入循环检测模块&#xff0c;此时number[a] == 0, b通过&#xff0c;进入critical</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>然后切换&#xff0c;</p>\n<p>number[a] = 1 &#xff08;因为此时number[b] 还未被赋值为1&#xff09;进入循环检测模块&#xff0c;此时&#xff08;nubmer[a], a&#xff09;&lt; (number[b], b)&#xff0c;也进入critical</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:35:04Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "ie7xy6atuuc1re", "created": "2016-04-25T01:35:04Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infc06mzrpn460", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T05:11:36Z", "uid": "ie7xy6atuuc1re", "created": "2016-04-25T05:11:36Z", "type": "feedback", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infjqnc7foz2ir", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>spoc问答题 <a href=\"https://github.com/zhengyk11/ucore_lab_docs/blob/master/07-1-spoc-discussion/07-1-spoc-discussion.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zhengyk11/ucore_lab_docs/blob/master/07-1-spoc-discussion/07-1-spoc-discussion.md</a></p>"}], "subject": "<p>2011011384 郑玉昆</p>\n<p>2013011375 茹逸中</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>设进程i的优先级高于进程j(即i&lt;j)&#xff0c;两个进程获得了相同的排队登记号(Number数组的元素值相等)。进程i在写Number[i]之前&#xff0c;被优先级低的进程j抢先获得了CPU时间片&#xff0c;这时进程j读取到的Number[i]为0&#xff0c;因此进程j进入了临界区. 随后进程i又获得CPU时间片&#xff0c;它读取到的Number[i]与Number[j]相等&#xff0c;且i&lt;j&#xff0c;因此进程i也进入了临界区.</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:35:31Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0c90j8pjf56sn", "created": "2016-04-25T01:35:31Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infc0rqxlvm5fn", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>2013011360 姜天健</p>\n<p>2013011370 桥本优</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Response777/OS2016/blob/master/os_spoc17/report.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Response777/OS2016/blob/master/os_spoc17/report.md</a></p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:35:56Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0dvatlio3g3ju", "created": "2016-04-25T01:35:56Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infc1auote33zq", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:36:45Z", "uid": "i0z7iyznm3owz", "created": "2016-04-25T01:36:45Z", "type": "feedback", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infc2cpjiwd2n8", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>2013011554 郭晓阳<br />2013011415 陈雨兰</p>"}], "subject": "<p>两个进程<br />T0, pid=0<br />T1, pid=1</p>\n<p>T0执行完max(...)&#xff0c;转到T1执行&#xff0c;T1执行完max(...)&#43;1&#xff0c;此时number[0]=0&#xff0c;number[1]=1&#xff0c;所以T1进入了临界区&#xff0c;在临界区中&#xff0c;转到T0执行&#xff0c;此时number[0]=1,另外T0的pid比T1的pid小&#xff0c;所以T0也进入了临界区。</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T01:37:23Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0ciknt4jrm39r", "created": "2016-04-25T01:37:23Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infc35u5iig75w", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>吴永宇 2013011424</p>\n<p>吴孟轩 2013011421</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/wu-yy/SPOC17/blob/master/%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E9%A2%98\" target=\"_blank\">课堂</a></p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T02:02:16Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0byevowhoc2ya", "created": "2016-04-25T02:02:16Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infcz6hests4gy", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 1, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T03:28:57Z", "uid": "i0byevowhoc2ya", "created": "2016-04-25T03:28:57Z", "type": "feedback", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infg2n3xw252z6", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bdxzwzz/os_spoc/blob/master/ex-07-1\" target=\"_blank\">ex-07-1</a></p>\n<p>完成的是</p>\n<p>2. &#xff08;spoc)了解race condition. 进入[race-condition代码目录](https://github.com/chyyuu/ucore_lab/tree/master/related_info/lab7/race-condition)。</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T05:06:51Z", "uid": "i0byevowhoc2ya", "created": "2016-04-25T05:06:51Z", "type": "feedback", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "infjkjwx5yk64g", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>然后spoc第三题也做了</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bdxzwzz/os_spoc/blob/master/ex-07-1\" target=\"_blank\">ex-07-1</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bdxzwzz/os_spoc/blob/master/Compare-And-Swap.s\" target=\"_blank\">Compare-And-Swap.s</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bdxzwzz/os_spoc/blob/master/Fetch-And-Add.s\" target=\"_blank\">Fetch-And-Add.s</a></p>"}], "subject": "<p>冯栩 2013011393</p>\n<p>王梓仲 2013011408</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>T0&#xff0c;pid = 0</p>\n<p>T1&#xff0c;pid = 1</p>\n<p>一开始number值都是0</p>\n<p>T0先做&#xff0c;做做做&#xff0c;做到算完max()&#43;1&#xff0c;然而并没有赋值&#xff0c;于是number[0]暂时为0&#xff0c;赋值后会是1</p>\n<p>这时切到T1&#xff0c;做做做&#xff0c;number[1]的赋值能做完&#xff0c;这样number[1]为1&#xff0c;到下面j为0时while的第一个判断(number[j] != 0)轻松不满足&#xff0c;于是进入critical section</p>\n<p>这时再切回T0&#xff0c;完成之前的赋值&#xff0c;number[0]为1&#xff0c;这样到下面while时由于number值相同&#xff0c;而T0的pid巨小无比&#xff0c;于是也进入critical section</p>\n<p>从而gg</p>\n<p>而加入choosing之后&#xff0c;上述过程中T1要等T0完成赋值才能进入第二个while&