 "2016-04-25T12:22:56Z", "uid": "i6swz3atggR", "created": "2016-04-25T12:22:56Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "infz5cnvk2e48g", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/junjiek/os_course_spoc_exercises/blob/master/10-spoc.md\" target=\"_blank\">spoc</a>问答题</p>"}], "subject": "<p>柯均洁 2012011335</p>\n<p>赵诚辉 2012011384</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Choosing问题&#xff0c;考虑两个进程&#xff1a;</p>\n<p>T0&#xff0c;pid = 0&#xff1b;T1&#xff0c;pid = 1</p>\n<p>一开始number[1] = number [0] = 0。</p>\n<p>T0先执行到max()&#43;1&#xff0c;还没赋值时切换到T1&#xff08;number[0]仍为0&#xff0c;赋值后会是1&#xff09;</p>\n<p>T1执行到number[1]赋值完&#xff08;number[1]为1&#xff09;&#xff0c;在循环内不满足(number[j] != 0)&#xff0c;于是T1进入临界区</p>\n<p>此时再切回T0&#xff0c;完成之前的赋值&#xff0c;number[0]为1。这时由于number值相同&#xff0c;而T0的pid更小&#xff0c;于是T0也进入临界区</p>\n<p>而加入choosing之后&#xff0c;T1要等T0赋值完成才能进入第二个while&#xff0c;所以能保证正确</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T12:50:22Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hxfr6dv2fy44k8", "created": "2016-04-25T12:50:22Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 1, "id": "ing04mp6blv7da", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>2011010870 杨凯峪 </p>\n<p>2012011487  徐梓哲</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/yangky11/os_course_spoc_exercises/blob/master/lec17.md\">https://github.com/yangky11/os_course_spoc_exercises/blob/master/lec17.md</a></p>\n<p></p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-25T13:56:37Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i6vkcot30qG", "created": "2016-04-25T13:56:37Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 1, "id": "ing2htr768u3wi", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>2012011370 魏洪浩<br />2012011279 李德旺</p>"}], "nr": 828, "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "status": "active", "tags": ["instructor-note", "课堂问答"], "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_l